Alexander MCDOUGALL (ID #I19842)

(male)

DEATH: BEF 1853?, Pennsylvania

Father: William MCDOUGALL (b. 23 SEP 1770, d. 17 JUN 1819)

Mother: Eleanor (Nelly) LIVINGSTON (b. 10 AUG 1777, d. 24 APR 1855)

Not named in the family partition deed of 1853, so probably dead by that time without issue. Jennie Patten seems to indicate he died in PA, but we wonder if she confused him with another Alexander.
